title: Republicans Reckon With Midterm Election Fallout
description: They may still win the House. But an underwhelming showing has the G.O.P. wrestling with what went wrong: Was it bad candidates, a bad message or Donald J. Trump?
dc:creator: Jonathan Weisman
media:credit: Jamie Kelter Davis for The New York Times
media:description: Former President Donald J. Trump held a rally in June outside Quincy, Ill. Candidates he endorsed lost the pivotal Senate race in Pennsylvania and key House and statewide races in Michigan, Ohio and North Carolina, among other places.
